<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 24 at 11:34PM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...A WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IS IN EFFECT...
Snow will continue to lift across the area overnight. This snow will
remain mainly light in intensity through 3 am, with additional
accumulation of up to one inch during this time. This will lead to
or maintain snow covered and slippery roadways. In addition,
visibility may drop below 1 mile at times. Use caution while
driving tonight and allow extra time to reach your destination. Be
prepared for variable road conditions and lowered visibilities.</description>
